Package: AMPHForecastSuite
Type: Package
Title: Suite of Tools for Infectious Disease Forecasting Pipeline and Hub
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("ACCIDDA", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "info@example.com")
    )
Description: A comprehensive suite of tools and helper functions to build and run 
    an infectious disease forecasting hub. This package facilitates the installation 
    and integration of key forecasting packages including hubverse packages, fable, 
    EpiEstim, EpiNow2, epidatr, and epiforecast. It provides helper functions that 
    translate data between different package formats to streamline forecasting workflows.
